{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/startServerCommunication","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Enables communication with Pushwoosh servers."}],"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"startServerCommunication","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Starts or resumes communication with Pushwoosh servers. This allows the SDK to send and receive","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"data including device registration, tags, push tokens, and analytics."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Call this method after the user has consented to data collection, or to re-enable","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"communication after it was previously stopped."}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Example","anchor":"Example","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Enable communication after GDPR consent:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["class ConsentManager {","","    func handleUserConsent(accepted: Bool) {","        if accepted {","            \/\/ User accepted data collection","            Pushwoosh.configure.startServerCommunication()","","            \/\/ Register for push after consent","            Pushwoosh.configure.registerForPushNotifications()","","            \/\/ Sync any pending user data","            syncPendingUserData()","","            L